600
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:26,550
Me, of course.

601
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,510
Chen Mo, don't forget.

602
00:30:34,630 --> 00:30:37,710
No door in this world can hold me back.

603
00:30:39,830 --> 00:30:41,870
Especially the door to your heart.

604
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:49,830
Bye.

605
00:30:53,350 --> 00:30:54,750
Xiao Dong, Chu Xia.

606
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,230
Why are you guys dating here?

607
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:57,830
It's not a date.

608
00:30:58,390 --> 00:30:59,710
I know.

609
00:31:03,150 --> 00:31:06,150
Still, for you to let them enter your lab,

610
00:31:06,150 --> 00:31:07,750
you're giving me face after all.

611
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:10,550
How absurd. Ridiculous.

612
00:31:11,030 --> 00:31:12,070
Is it ridiculous?

613
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,550
If it is ridiculous,

614
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:18,870
why did you pick me up from work?

615
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:20,150
Who picked you up?

616
00:31:20,430 --> 00:31:22,510
Who'd know that I'd bump into you
at the supermarket that day?

617
00:31:23,670 --> 00:31:26,350
A supermarket trip takes just about five minutes.

618
00:31:26,430 --> 00:31:28,030
There are 24 hours in a day.

619
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:30,830
So, the probability of us meeting by chance is 3 out of 1000.

620
00:31:30,870 --> 00:31:32,990
Do you believe in such a coincidence?

621
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:36,590
Just because the odds are low
doesn't mean it wouldn't happen.

622
00:31:36,710 --> 00:31:38,390
It still happened despite the low odds.

623
00:31:38,390 --> 00:31:41,190
Are you hinting that we share a destiny?

624
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:43,190
The odds of a satellite hitting Earth are low too.

625
00:31:43,190 --> 00:31:45,350
If that happens, would you call it destiny or disaster?

626
00:31:45,540 --> 00:31:47,990
If it's a disaster,

627
00:31:48,470 --> 00:31:50,110
then why did you buy me medicine that day?

628
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:52,670
Who bought you medicine?

629
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:54,870
You snatched my phone and bought it yourself.

630
00:31:55,870 --> 00:31:58,630
How can I snatch a phone from a strong man like you?

631
00:31:58,630 --> 00:32:01,630
Even if I could, how would I know your WeChat password?

632
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:04,390
Even if I knew the password,
how would I know your payment code?

633
00:32:04,550 --> 00:32:06,430
Face it, you bought me the medicine.

634
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:08,470
The way you keep going on and on is annoying!

635
00:32:08,470 --> 00:32:11,060
I bought you the medicine so that I could clear my head!

636
00:32:11,150 --> 00:32:12,630
I know you love it when it's clear.

637
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:14,550
That's why I came here without even applying makeup.

638
00:32:14,550 --> 00:32:16,230
That's not what I mean by "clear".

639
00:32:16,230 --> 00:32:17,990
Besides, your face looks so smooth today.

640
00:32:17,990 --> 00:32:19,830
How are you not applying any makeup? This isn't scientific.

641
00:32:19,830 --> 00:32:22,060
415 is a place that is based on science.

642
00:32:22,060 --> 00:32:23,030
You're not scientific.

643
00:32:23,350 --> 00:32:26,310
You can even tell if I'm wearing makeup or not.

644
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,830
How annoying!

645
00:32:27,910 --> 00:32:29,670
You're a role model, Aunt Wei Wei.

646
00:32:32,310 --> 00:32:33,060
Just you wait.

647
00:32:34,630 --> 00:32:35,190
Chen Mo.

648
00:32:37,750 --> 00:32:38,340
Chen Mo.

649
00:32:38,340 --> 00:32:39,110
Wait!

650
00:32:39,510 --> 00:32:40,430
Stand behind the yellow line.

651
00:32:42,590 --> 00:32:43,790
Is this some kind of checkpoint?

652
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:46,190
Besides, where's the yellow line?

653
00:32:47,310 --> 00:32:48,310
Miss Shen Wei Wei.

654
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:49,870
I'm warning you.

655
00:32:50,630 --> 00:32:52,230
You are seriously affecting my work.

656
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:01,310
Chen Mo, speak the truth.

657
00:33:03,150 --> 00:33:04,390
Are you scared of me?

658
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:06,910
What a joke.

659
00:33:07,150 --> 00:33:09,430
415 is my lab. Why would I be scared of you?

660
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:14,510
If you're not scared of me, then why do you keep...

661
00:33:15,270 --> 00:33:16,030
Burping?

662
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:18,710
