from eating too many nuts this morning.

663
00:33:18,710 --> 00:33:20,700
You're already tempted.

664
00:33:20,700 --> 00:33:22,390
Still trying to play hard to get.

665
00:33:23,310 --> 00:33:24,790
Don't you feel yourself burning from being so close to me?

666
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:25,950
Keep your distance, will you?

667
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:27,950
Are you tired?

668
00:33:28,230 --> 00:33:31,070
You've gone round and round so many times in my heart.

669
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:39,070
Okay, I'll buy your insurance.

670
00:33:39,390 --> 00:33:40,550
I'll buy, okay?

671
00:33:41,230 --> 00:33:42,070
Can you leave now?

672
00:33:43,990 --> 00:33:45,430
What in the world do you want?

673
00:33:45,950 --> 00:33:50,110
When you're in love, you act faster than your heart.

674
00:33:52,230 --> 00:33:54,030
[When you're in love, you act faster than your heart.]

675
00:33:55,230 --> 00:33:56,230
[That's love, right?]

676
00:34:20,310 --> 00:34:22,989
Do you feel anything like a hint of happiness?

677
00:34:26,870 --> 00:34:27,989
Or the taste of a little sunshine?

678
00:34:32,790 --> 00:34:34,350
What about the taste of falling in love?

679
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:42,219
I've tried all five flavours here.

680
00:34:42,219 --> 00:34:45,510
I couldn't taste anything like happiness, sunshine

681
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,830
or falling in love.

682
00:34:47,670 --> 00:34:49,150
I only feel like something's stuck in my throat now.

683
00:34:50,470 --> 00:34:51,750
That's strange.

684
00:34:58,190 --> 00:34:59,030
You're giving up?

685
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:03,190
The phrase "give up" doesn't exist in my life.

686
00:35:09,350 --> 00:35:11,830
Summer's Kiss, oh Summer's Kiss.

687
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:13,750
What should we do with you?

688
00:35:13,950 --> 00:35:14,910
Summer's Kiss.

689
00:35:17,830 --> 00:35:19,030
