690
00:35:20,350 --> 00:35:21,630
Seriously, a kiss?

691
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:25,150
Think about it. What's it called?

692
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:26,220
It's called Summer's...

693
00:35:27,190 --> 00:35:27,790
Kiss.

694
00:35:30,870 --> 00:35:32,380
This isn't a good idea.

695
00:35:32,990 --> 00:35:33,990
I...

696
00:36:04,990 --> 00:36:06,310
Just try it, then.

697
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:21,590
Nana.

698
00:36:21,910 --> 00:36:24,990
I want to know how a summer's kiss is like too.

699
00:36:32,910 --> 00:36:34,230
Is this it, Summer's Kiss?

700
00:36:35,070 --> 00:36:36,550
It just looks like a fancy cake.

701
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:37,710
Is it really that delicious?

702
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:48,590
Chu Xia.

703
00:36:49,270 --> 00:36:50,070
You did it.

704
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:52,750
You're awesome!

705
00:36:52,830 --> 00:36:55,150
This tastes exactly the same as the cake ten years ago.

706
00:36:55,150 --> 00:36:56,630
How did you recall it?

707
00:36:57,070 --> 00:36:58,710
Yeah, didn't you lose your memory?

708
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:03,580
You could even remember the recipe for Summer's Kiss.

709
00:37:03,750 --> 00:37:05,340
Then, if you use the same method,

710
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:07,430
do you think you can remember the other recipes you had?

711
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,110
No.

712
00:37:11,390 --> 00:37:12,150
Xu Xiao Dong.

713
00:37:15,230 --> 00:37:16,310
Lei Chu Xia.

714
00:37:17,950 --> 00:37:20,270
What do you have to do with how she remembered the cake?

715
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:24,670
What does he have to do with how you remembered the cake?

716
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:28,990
You'd still babble even if I stuff your mouth.

717
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:36,230
They...

718
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:54,030
Xiao Dong.

719
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:57,380
Didn't I taste this at your house before?

720
00:37:58,350 --> 00:37:59,140
My house?

721
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:14,230
Xiao Dong.

722
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:16,230
