725
00:38:29,310 --> 00:38:30,470
Look at me, so forgetful.

726
00:38:30,870 --> 00:38:33,630
I'm so busy with work until I got all muddled up.

727
00:38:34,310 --> 00:38:35,430
Then, why don't you try this...

728
00:38:35,950 --> 00:38:37,390
