729
00:38:40,180 --> 00:38:40,910
You can have it.

730
00:39:07,870 --> 00:39:08,550
What is it?

731
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:12,630
Xiao Dong, do you remember the app we worked on together?

732
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:15,190
No, I mean the app you tweaked.

733
00:39:16,700 --> 00:39:17,670
