754
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:11,670
Both of us keep quiet, and no one will notice.

755
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:17,030
Come on, you're just as handsome as I am.

756
00:40:19,830 --> 00:40:20,670
Can you do it?

757
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:23,260
Okay.

758
00:40:23,630 --> 00:40:24,390
